            <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-orange-500">What is SGST, CGST, IGST and UTGST?</h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mt-4">
                Under the GST law, the central government will collect CGST and SGST or only IGST respectively,
