            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 text-center mt-4">
                The full form of IGST is Integrated Goods and Services Tax. Under GST, IGST applies to all
                interstate
                supplies of goods/services or across two or more states/UTs.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc mt-4 ml-12 lg:ml-28 text-lg text-gray-600">
                <li>Exports are zero-rated.</li>
                <li>Tax is shared between Central and State governments.</li>
